{"id":"azubah","term":"Azubah","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>Deserted. (1.) The wife of Caleb (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:18\">1 Chr. 2:18</a>, <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 2:19\">19</a>).</p>\n<p>(2.) The daughter of Shilhi, and mother of king Jehoshaphat (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Kings 22:42\">1 Kings 22:42</a>).</p>\n\u0000","refs":["1 Chronicles 2:18","1 Chronicles 2:19","1 Kings 22:42"]}